best_drivers_summary <- FERR %>%
  group_by(season, driver) %>%
  summarise(total_points = sum(points), .groups = 'drop') %>%
  group_by(season) %>%
  slice_max(order_by = total_points, n = 1) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  select(season, driver, total_points)

season_1 <- FERR0 %>%
  filter(season == 1)
season_1_data <- season_1 %>%
  group_by(driver) %>%
  summarise(
    total_points = sum(points),
    average_points = mean(points),
    frequency = n()
    ) %>%
  arrange(desc(total_points))

ggplot(season_1_data, aes(x = average_points, y = total_points)) +

mod_1 <- lm(total_points ~ average_points, data = season_1_data)
summary_1 <- summary(mod_1)
r_squared_1 <- summary_1$r.squared

season_1_long <- pivot_longer(season_1_data, 
                                cols = c(total_points, average_points), 
                                names_to = "variable", 
                                values_to = "value")
ggplot(season_1_long, aes(x = variable, y = value, fill = variable)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  labs(title = "Boxplot of Season One Statistics",
       x = "Variable",
       y = "Value") +
  theme_minimal()

 selected_season <- FERR %>%
  filter(season == "1") %>%
  group_by(driver) %>%
  summarize(avg_points = mean(points, na.rm = TRUE))

selected_season_with_freq <- merge(selected_season, freq_season_1, by = "driver", all.x = TRUE)
selected_season_with_freq$driver <- reorder(selected_season_with_freq$driver,
selected_season_with_freq$avg_points, FUN = function(x) -x)




ggplot(selected_season_with_freq, aes(x = driver, y = avg_points)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", fill = "skyblue") +
  labs(
    x = "Driver",
    y = "Average Points",
    title = "Average Points per Driver in Season 1"
  ) +
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1)) + 
  scale_x_discrete(labels = function(x) paste(x, " (Freq:", selected_season_with_freq$Freq[match(x, selected_season_with_freq$driver)], ")"))
